================================================================================
1. OVERVIEW
================================================================================

X-PIE performs automated structure modeling of protein complexes through the
following steps:

    Step 1: Crosslink analysis and interface clustering
    Step 2: Generation of distance restraints and sampling scripts
    Step 3: PDB/PSF preparation and hydrogen rebuilding
    Step 4: Simulated annealing via XPLOR-NIH

The pipeline is implemented as a single Python script (x-pie-modeling.py) that
orchestrates the full workflow. Both interactive (recommended for first-time
users) and batch modes are supported.



