------------------------

X-PIE requires access to the XPLOR binary and topology/parameter files.
After installing XPLOR-NIH, note the following paths:

    <xplor_home>/toppar/topallhdg_new.pro
    <xplor_home>/toppar/parallhdg_new.pro
    <xplor_home>/toppar/toph11.pep

These paths will be configured in x-pie.cfg (see Section 7).


